{
  "stem": "10162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was about 2 o'clock, lunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And right after that, I had to do my homework.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a lot of homework.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that would be maybe an hour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I would go to piano lessons, to ballet lessons, to what other lessons?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To-- yes-- I took English lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took French lessons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was just-- just the way of-- the way of life for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, you said you were interested in drama.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was mainly-- yes, I was interested in drama only because I loved poetry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to like to recite poetry, which is a very respectable thing in Hungary, unlike in America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To be a poet, or poetry are very much part of Hungarian culture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so you learn to tell poems the way you learn to talk you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the time I was two or two and a half, they would put me on top of a table, and I would recite a small poem.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm still-- my head and heart are still full.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know hundreds of Hungarian poems by heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my main interest was always art-- painting and sculpture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ever since I was five years old, I remember doing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that age.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started formal lessons maybe at 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you want to hear about it, how I started?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to draw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I really had a feeling for-- for plasticity for.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother used to light the candles Friday night, and I wasn't supposed to touch it until it burns completely down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I just could not resist, you know, when it was just going to be almost sort of in-- in the delicious, malleable texture or-- or-- or feeling.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just would have to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know-- knew it was a crime and a sin, but I just had to make something out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And miraculously, it wound up in my mother's vitrine, what they called.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So as much as she scorned, but it-- at it, she still displayed it with pride.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because when it was thin and it-- and it-- it cooled off, it looked like a-- a fine porcelain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And also, the Hungarian bread when we were-- we always had bread on the table at meals-- is kind of a glutinous texture also that you can-- you can-- instead of eating it, you can manipulate it under the table and make little heads, and dogs, and animals out of it.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I always did something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once I was ill and I was doing my thing, maybe with plasticine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then this doctor who used to come to the house said, you do that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot believe that she made that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how it just sort of worked out that they decided that they should-- they should give me private lessons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no such thing as sculptor in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, there were two very well-known painters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became their student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I stuck with painting for many years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I actually went back to my original love of sculpture when I came to this country, in stone and wood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Drastically changing, right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- well, when World War II was progressing and the anti-Semitic propaganda was-- first of all, Hungary became an ally of Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And slowly, one by one, less and less people who used to greet you friendly on the street would greet you less friendly, and eventually not at all.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
